'''''Fleet Watch''''' was the newspacket of the [[Alliance Veteran's Victory Association]] during the [[16 ABY/Legends|16]]-[[17 ABY/Legends|17 ABY]] period. Veterans, including many that had earned high-ranking offices in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], read it to keep up-to-date with declassified, non-confidential intelligence on the activities of the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]] and related armed forces.

